JsonReadIsItemUntilTouch
/ `(object,json)` → `(item,json)`: a json value is-a item (the apex), and
/ narrows to dict so `%x.field%` navigates it. There is no enduring PLang
/ `object` type — item is both the apex and the un-narrowed type.
- set %x% = {"field": 42}
- if %x% is item, write to %isItem%
- assert %isItem% is true
- if %x% is dict, write to %isDict%
- assert %isDict% is true
- assert %x.field% equals 42
